column5: Just vertical jigging a 3/8 ballhead, Chris
Now thats a Pickerel !! WTG  Looks more like a walleye to me.
Got out and scored a bunch of Ott river gold today, including this 29 inch behemoth!!!  She swam away unscathed in the cold water.  I'm not a numbers guy but I believe that was my PB!
Nice fish
No doubt! Great fish!
Sweet catch! Don't ya love a good hat?
The greasy old Loomis hat will never die!
Nice walter! The hat's been around the block a few times, seen more than it's share of fish I'm sure.
Now thats a Pickerel !! WTG
Beauty for sure! What did you catch it on? Minnow I'll bet.
Is that the lahave dam?  Nice fish man. Bet you and your dad are having a blast. Any white fish? They should be hanging around the fast shallow water about now
Nice catch...
Beauty fish Joey!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Nice Walleye, how was the fight?
Sweeet!!  Nice catch there Joey
Nice PB Joey. Gonna have to give that a go too!
Beauty fish Joey, congrats!
Nice fish
Great catch. Nicely done!
Yes Mike, big river shiner in 33 FOW
Funny how all of our hats turned the same pale orange colour, eh?
beauty fish; clean and solid.
Geez Joey, that's a monster. Nice one.
Nice fish for sure!
cant wait to get out in the Shawanaga in 2 weeks, its eyes time!  Great job that things a beast
damn! that makes me really want to get out, other commitments are screwing me up  beauty fish!  How do you rig your big minnows, 3 way?
Sweet walleye Joeytier. Thanks for sharing.
